Class Summary
AbstractConnectorListener Abstract basis for all platform dependant connectorLinstener implementations.
Connector Base class for all platform specific connectors.
ConnectorMessageEvent Event object a connector will use when it fires a message received or sent event.
ConnectorStatusEvent This event will be raised when the connector instance has a change in status.

Enum Summary
Connector.Status Enumeration of the connector status.
 

Exception Summary
ConnectorException Exception class which connectors can throw.
LoadLibraryException This exception will be thrown when loading a library failed.
NotAttachedException This exception will be thrown when a command is sent to a connector but when the connector isn't connected.
TimeOutException This exception is thrown when a connector is working with a timeout.
